Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.80,0:00:06.81,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you desire freedom and rights, Hohenheim?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:11.05,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Do you plan to let your life end as a slave,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.05,0:00:13.15,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,without even obtaining your basic rights as a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:19.23,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,If so, you might as well be living in this stuffy flask.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.08,0:00:33.72,Default,Fath,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:35.02,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.02,0:00:36.34,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Finish him, Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:39.76,Default,Fath,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I, someone who has obtained God,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:41.60,Default,Fath,0000,0000,0000,,being defeated by the bare hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:45.07,Default,Fath,0000,0000,0000,,...of a mere human alchemist?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.05,0:00:57.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:00:58.45,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:01:00.05,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,You showed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.71,0:01:24.52,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Man the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:26.02,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting swept away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:27.44,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,M-My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.55,0:01:30.06,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:34.28,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Philosopher's stone!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:43.37,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your philosopher's stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.23,0:01:46.66,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:48.12,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Greed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:50.46,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, you're going to get yourself dragged in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:51.29,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:52.64,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.64,0:01:56.59,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,In order for me to become the Emperor, I need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:57.87,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,That's just impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,0:02:00.87,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I was born from Father to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:04.00,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,The force that's pulling me toward him is stronger than the one pulling me toward Lin Yao!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:05.47,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing can be done!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.47,0:02:07.28,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up, Greed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:08.34,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Keep trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:11.48,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:13.52,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,My body...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:18.36,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,God dammit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.02,0:02:24.94,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's a few ranks lower than being the king of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:27.20,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess I wouldn't mind becoming the Emperor of Xing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.11,0:02:30.58,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna fight together, partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:32.58,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,That's the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:37.46,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:40.17,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,And this is goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:43.97,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for you to be absorbed by him along with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:47.53,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hang on, Greed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:51.32,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,You just said that we were going to fight together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:54.11,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,This is foul play, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:57.99,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you never told lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:02:59.55,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,You can't let it end like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:03.74,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,You totally fell for it though, shitty brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:09.25,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,That was my first and final lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:12.74,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Lan Fan has a philosopher's stone with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:15.47,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Take it home with you, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:17.00,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:19.76,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:23.34,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Greed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:25.22,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Lan Fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:28.43,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:32.85,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Greed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Greed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:39.81,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you, Greed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.44,0:03:46.28,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to free myself from an annoying brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:55.94,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you revolt against your father, Greed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:59.17,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Just going through a late puberty, pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:04.09,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,With this carbonization ability you gave me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:07.60,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn us into the most brittle form of carbon, charcoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.30,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.60,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Begone, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:19.78,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Greed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:26.16,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I guess this is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:37.82,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look in the damn mirror, brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:40.67,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Friends are connected by the soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:42.89,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you'd forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:47.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Want to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:49.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got nowhere else to go, come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:56.35,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Man, both Lin and the midget totally made a fool out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:01.61,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,That was plenty...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:05.59,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that was enough for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:08.87,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need anything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:16.62,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Peace out, soul... brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:43.75,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.23,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,My stones...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.66,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,My philosopher's stones...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:05:59.94,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:01.75,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:07.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to where you were born,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:10.68,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dwarf in the Flask, Homunculus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:21.15,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:24.65,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to learn everything about this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:31.20,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to live freely in this vast world without being bound by anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:34.12,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:47.39,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.56,0:06:51.05,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you become mine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:54.18,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,God, what are you unhappy with?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:56.93,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,Because you don't believe in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.03,0:07:04.80,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,You were born from humans after stealing other's power,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.80,0:07:07.69,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,and yet, you were just clinging on to God the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:10.52,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't grown up at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:16.33,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think you'd be able to surpass humans if you let go of your seven desires?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:17.99,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:21.63,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to become a perfect being!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:24.04,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to learn everything about this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.29,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with wanting that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:28.21,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with desiring it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:30.97,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with wishing for it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:36.02,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:38.52,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:40.44,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:43.57,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:49.67,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the existence which you all refer to as "The World."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:53.00,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,And "Universe," and "God,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:57.91,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,and "Truth," and "All," and "One."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:01.94,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,And I am also yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:07.41,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,Truth is what gives one the most fitting form of despair to insure them not to become conceited.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:13.42,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,He gives humans the most fitting form of despair to make sure humans don't become conceited.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:15.68,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,That is Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:23.15,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, I'll also give you despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:32.53,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:33.86,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:39.53,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! I don't want to be bound there forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:47.71,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:49.65,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:51.91,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,Despair to the ones who become swelled with pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:54.42,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,What else should I have done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:57.19,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end you desired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:08:59.50,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,What should I have done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:10.44,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,You probably foresaw the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:22.67,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,What? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:24.04,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Did we win?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:24.84,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:29.79,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,But... Alphonse has yet to come back from the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:33.53,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm so sorry...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:35.60,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:36.98,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It was Al's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:40.15,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Ed, we have a toll.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:43.56,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Use it, it's a philosopher's stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:45.59,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Use this to get Al back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.26,0:09:49.56,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:56.74,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We promised we'd never use a philosopher's stone to get our bodies back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:06.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:08.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There HAS to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:09.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Think...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:11.17,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Think!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:12.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop thinking!{dooon't stop believin'}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:14.82,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Edward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.21,0:10:21.16,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Use my life to bring Alphonse back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:24.84,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I've got just enough life left for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:28.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:29.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:34.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's our own fault that we lost our bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:39.10,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I've said so many times that we won't use other's lives to get Al back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:42.20,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, why the hell do YOU have to give your life up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:43.78,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:47.79,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,It's not about needs or reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:50.40,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,You two are precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:52.79,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I want the both of you to live happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:59.31,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm partially to blame for what happened to your bodies, since I left you to care for yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:03.99,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:07.56,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I've lived enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:11.82,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Let me do something father-like for just this last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:21.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous, you good-for-nothing dad!{I know this sounds like shit, but 'dad' has to be in this line somehow; you'll see later on in the script. Make it sound better?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:23.37,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever say something like that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:25.32,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll punch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:44.16,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Edward...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:49.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Think...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:50.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Think!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:53.71,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't I supposed to be the youngest state alchemist of all time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:58.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I can use alchemy without a transmutation circle because I saw Truth, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:00.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:02.20,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:13.87,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure a lot of people are waiting for the day when you two get your bodies back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:17.88,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,If there's a possibility, you should move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:22.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:25.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There... There has to be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.63,0:12:26.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:45.38,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Al...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:47.02,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Al...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:49.24,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:53.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,May is crying so much for Al...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:13:01.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Zampano, Donkey Kong, and everyone from Briggs...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:06.13,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Major, Lin, Lan Fan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:09.64,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Master, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:20.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,May, step away for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:49.55,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:53.61,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,A human transmutation circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:56.56,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:14:02.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The last transmutation that the Fullmetal Alchemist will ever do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:10.91,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:12.03,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:14.29,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Edward Elric!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:33.82,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,So you came to get your brother back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:37.99,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,But how are you going to drag an entire human out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:39.51,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,What will you sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:41.80,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,Your entire body?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:46.69,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There's something huge right here that I can sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:55.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This is MY Gate of Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:59.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Which means I can do whatever I want with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:00.71,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.02,0:15:06.71,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,So that was your plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:11.49,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,But are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:16.40,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose your Gate of Truth,\Nyou'll never be able to use alchemy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:18.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:24.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, all of alchemy is on the other side of this gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:27.98,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to it, I was manipulated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:34.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I was shown the Truth, and believed that I could solve everything with alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:37.57,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:40.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I was just being arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:44.50,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to become an ordinary human who can't use alchemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:49.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to "become" anything. I've always been an ordinary human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:54.69,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a puny human who couldn't even save a girl who was turned into a chimera.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:59.06,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,So you're sure you don't mind getting rid of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:00.00,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:00.71,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:01.68,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Edward!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:02.23,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:03.63,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Edward Elric!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:04.25,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:05.12,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Edward!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:05.83,Default,Pinako,0000,0000,0000,,Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:07.46,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:11.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I lose alchemy, I'll still have my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:14.78,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,Correct, alchemist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:18.08,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,You've defeated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:21.66,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,Take everything you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:27.67,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,The back door is over that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:30.05,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,Edward Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.24,0:16:44.69,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You were so reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:47.94,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Ditto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:57.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go back. Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.06,0:16:57.95,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.21,0:17:16.34,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, he's awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:18.22,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,You okay, Alphonse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.44,0:17:21.88,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Zampano and Mr. Darius...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:22.95,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:26.42,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:28.41,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:32.87,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:34.23,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:37.61,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,So warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:40.13,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Al...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:42.50,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Alphonse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:43.62,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,May!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:46.62,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:50.81,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:52.63,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I made you do something you didn't want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.35,0:17:55.37,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, May.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:01.14,Default,Cas,0000,0000,0000,,To those who are listening to Radio Capital:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:06.14,Default,Cas,0000,0000,0000,,Today, the squadrons led by Major General Armstrong and Colonel Mustang
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:08.85,Default,Cas,0000,0000,0000,,captured Central Headquarters, assembly, and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:13.65,Default,Cas,0000,0000,0000,,This was all in order to halt the actions of the upper echelon of the army;
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:18.90,Default,Cas,0000,0000,0000,,they were planning a massive alchemy experiment that would sacrifice a great number of our citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.92,0:18:25.55,Default,Cas,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the masterminds who were planning on carrying out this evil experiment,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:28.29,Default,Cas,0000,0000,0000,,Brigadier General Clemin and Brigadier General Edison were captured,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:32.29,Default,Cas,0000,0000,0000,,and the soldiers who used to be under their command were disarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:37.71,Default,Cas,0000,0000,0000,,Führer President King Bradley and his son, Selim,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:41.08,Default,Cas,0000,0000,0000,,lost their lives in the midst of the confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:49.12,Default,Cas,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel Mustang has voiced his intention to carry on the will of the Führer President and to keep our nation safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:52.76,Default,Cas,0000,0000,0000,,and that he'll consult with all whom it may concern about future measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:02.83,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who gave me blood, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:08.54,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you desire freedom and rights, Hohenheim?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:12.50,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Then what does happiness mean to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:16.50,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... I won't ask for anything too extravagant,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:20.82,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess I'd be happy if I could somehow leave this flask.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:29.02,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, Dwarf in the Flask, Homunculus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:34.17,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,You were born from my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:37.52,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:43.58,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hohenheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:48.57,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Both of your children have been safely hospitalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:51.96,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:55.17,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,No, I should be the one thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:20:01.70,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Edward Elric and Alphonse Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:06.15,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for those two boys, this country would have fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:08.68,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:16.44,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:03.74,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home, Trisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:12.24,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Edward called me "Dad."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:15.30,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Though there was a "good-for-nothing" in front of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:26.01,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought that it would be backbreaking to continue living longer than everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.74,0:21:29.90,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,But by meeting you and our sons,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.90,0:21:34.02,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to truly appreciate the fact that I was alive, from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:37.15,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,It was a fulfilling life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:41.81,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... it was more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.08,0:21:45.76,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Trisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:51.81,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:56.40,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,...somehow, I still want to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.27,0:22:01.27,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I really am a good-for-nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:10.77,Default,Pinako,0000,0000,0000,,Hohenheim!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:14.38,Default,Pinako,0000,0000,0000,,What, you came home?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:21.96,Default,Pinako,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:26.69,Default,Pinako,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a dead person look so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.46,0:24:01.79,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.79,0:24:05.18,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Finale, The End of a Journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.96,0:24:10.41,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Take a step forward into the world called "life."
